Text: What a shame!  A/V = 10, but it's nothing but an Eddie Murphy ass-kiss fest.  He's a monster talent, but a roast would have gone miles more!  Flava Flav got roasted and he's now more famous for it.  Makes you think that Hollywood is afraid of making fun of Eddie - so what?
Is there an uncensored version available? Those beeps suck and ruin it.
